<document>
    <header>
        <title>Setting up Northern Sámi keyboard and Northern Sámi as input language
        in Windows 10</title>
    </header>
    <body>

        <p>We show how to set up Northern Sámi as an input language. When one
        chooses Northern Sámi as an input language, the spelling checker will
        automatically be run in Northern Sámi when the Divvun tools are installed.</p>
  
        <ol>
            <li>Go to the <strong>Start</strong> menu, and click on
                <strong>Settings</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10-start_menu-en.png" alt="Startmeny"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Click on <strong>Time &amp; language</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10-prefs-en.png" alt="Kontrollpanel"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Click <strong>Add a language</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10-prefs-time_and_lang-en.png" alt="Språk" /></p>
            </li>
            <li>Choose <strong>Davvisámegiella</strong> by clicking the name:
                <p><img src="images/win10-prefs-add-sme-en.png" alt="Legg til språk"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Choose the variant of <strong>Davvisámegiella</strong> you want:
                <p><img src="images/win10-prefs-add-sme-norway-no.png" alt="Regionale varianter"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Click <strong>Davvisámegiella</strong> followed by <strong>Alternatives</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10-prefs-modify-sme-no.png" alt="Språk etter å ha valgt nordsamisk"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Click <strong>Add Keyboard</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10-prefs-add-keyboard-no.png" alt="Språkalternativer"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Choose <strong>Samisk, utvidet Norge</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10-prefs-add-sme-extended-norway-no.png" alt="Inndatametode"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Select <strong>Norsk med samisk</strong> and click <strong>Remove</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10-prefs-remove-norw_with_sami-keyboard-no.png"
                alt="Språkalternativer: Fjern norsk med samisk"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Now you have <strong>Davvisámegiella (Norga)</strong> as an
                input language with the keyboard <strong>Samisk, utvidet Norge</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10-keyboard-done-sme-no.png"
                alt="Språk med nordsamisk ferdigvalgt"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>To switch between the keyboard and thus language, press
                <strong>Alt+Shift</strong> until the Norther Sami keyboard is
                activated:
                <p><img src="images/win10-switching-keyboards-sme-no.png"
                alt="Språk med nordsamisk ferdigvalgt"/></p>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </body>
</document>
